                <head>The Great Question of the Day</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Great Question facing Virginians is the disposition of public lands, and
                    what to do with the accumulated funds. VA is interested because it ceded a lot
                    of thease lands to the Federal government. Also, VA needs money. Feels like they
                    aren't beeing fairly treated.</summary>
            </div>
